These are Puzzles for 5x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-1::.
There 4 different types of food: peach, corn, apricot, cherry
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, photography, magic-tricks, reading
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: western, animation, satire, fantasy
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: jazz, r&b, metal, house
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, goat, fish, hedgehog
 1. the person watching western movies is on the right of the person eating corn##1
 2. the person who's hobby is photography is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 3. the person who's hobby is reading is on the left of the fan of r&b##1
 4. the owner of the goat is on the right of the owner of the rabbit##1
 5. the fan of jazz is the person eating peach##1
 6. the fan of r&b is on the left of the owner of the rabbit##1
 7. the fan of metal is on the right of the person eating peach##1
 8. the person eating apricot is on the left of the person who's hobby is rock-climbing##1
 9. the person watching satire movies is the person eating peach##1
10. the owner of the fish is the person watching animation movies##1
11. the person who's hobby is rock-climbing is on the right of the owner of the hedgehog##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3      |     4      |
| Food          | corn    | apricot      | peach  | cherry     |
| Hobby         | reading    | magic-tricks   | rock-climbing | photography      |
| Movie-Genre   | animation       | western | satire     | fantasy    |
| Music-Genre   | house | r&b         | jazz  | metal    |
| Pet           | fish      | hedgehog       | rabbit | goat |

