.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: cola, lemonade, water, sprite
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: scientific, thriller, western, adventure
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, soul, dubstep, country
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, chinchilla, guinea-pig, lizard
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: climbing, rugby, cycling, volleyball
 1. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person who's sport is climbing##1
 2. the fan of pop is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1
 3. the person who's sport is volleyball is on the right of the owner of the lizard##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the far right##1
 5. the person drinking cola is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1
 6. the person who's sport is cycling is on the right of the person drinking water##1
 7. the fan of country is on the right of the person watching scientific movies##1
 8. the owner of the chinchilla is the fan of country##1
 9. the person watching western movies is the fan of dubstep##1
10. the fan of pop is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking water is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3     |       4       |
| Beverage      | lemonade      | cola     | water    | sprite |
| Movie-Genre   | scientific | thriller   | western   | adventure           |
| Music-Genre   | soul  | country     | dubstep    | pop         |
| Pet           | lizard         | chinchilla | guinea-pig     | goldfish        |
| Sport         | climbing     | volleyball  | rugby | cycling       |

