.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-3::.
There 4 different types of food: tomato, cherry, banana, orange
There are 4 different nationalities: pakistani, canadian, argentine, polish
4 different pets are kept: dog, cat, goldfish, hamster
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: biathlon, swimming, lacrosse, rugby
The people use 4 different means of transport: train, motorbike, bus, scooter
 1. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the far left##1
 2. the person who's sport is swimming is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 3. the person eating banana is the owner of the hamster##1
 4. the person eating cherry is on the right of the person driving the scooter##1
 5. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the right of the person eating orange##1
 6. the person driving the scooter is the person eating banana##1
 7. the argentine is on the left of the person driving the scooter##1
 8. the person driving the train is on the right of the person driving the bus##1
 9. the polish is the owner of the cat##1
10. the canadian is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
11. the person driving the scooter is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
12. the person eating banana is on the right of the person who's sport is swimming##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2       |    3    |       4       |
| Food          | tomato    | orange      | banana  | cherry   |
| Nationality   | polish     | argentine      | canadian | pakistani      |
| Pet           | cat       | dog         | hamster  | goldfish         |
| Sport         | biathlon | swimming | lacrosse  | rugby |
| Transport     | bus       | train         | scooter   | motorbike        |

