.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-4::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: 7up, mirinda, milk, lemonade
There 4 different types of food: carrot, zucchini, artichoke, pumpkin
There are 4 different nationalities: german, pakistani, american, russian
4 different pets are kept: mouse, lizard, bird, rat
The people use 4 different means of transport: van, train, bus, motorbike
 1. the owner of the lizard is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
 2. the person eating pumpkin is on the left of the person driving the train##1
 3. the person driving the train is on the right of the owner of the rat##1
 4. the owner of the bird is on the far right##1
 5. the person driving the van is on the far left##1
 6. the person driving the bus is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 7. the russian is on the far right##1
 8. the person eating pumpkin is on the right of the american##1
 9. the pakistani is on the left of the person eating carrot##1
10. the person drinking 7up is on the far right##1
11. the person drinking milk is on the far left##1
12. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person eating zucchini##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |     3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | milk   | lemonade   | mirinda      | 7up     |
| Food          | artichoke     | carrot   | pumpkin | zucchini |
| Nationality   | pakistani | american | german   | russian       |
| Pet           | lizard       | mouse      | rat     | bird |
| Transport     | van    | bus     | motorbike     | train     |

