 2. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the far left##1
 3. the chinese is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the hamster is the person eating peas##1
 5. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the person eating carrot##1
 6. the writer is on the far right##1
 7. the owner of the rabbit is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 8. the owner of the guinea-pig is the chef##1
 9. the person eating cucumber is the owner of the rabbit##1
10. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
11. the indonesian is on the right of the owner of the guinea-pig##1
12. the entrepreneur is on the far left##1
13. the indonesian is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
14. the brazilian is on the right of the japanese##1

.:: Answer ::.
