.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-6::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: rock-climbing, camping, reading, hiking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: crime, adventure, horror, time-travel
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, argentine, mexican, malaysian
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, skateboarding, parkour, golf
The people use 4 different means of transport: helicopter, train, taxi, quad-bike
 1. the person who's sport is parkour is on the right of the mexican##1
 2. the person who's sport is golf is on the right of the person who's sport is parkour##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is the person who's sport is golf##1
 4. the person watching adventure movies is on the right of the person driving the taxi##1
 5. the person watching time-travel movies is on the left of the dutch##1
 6. the dutch is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 7. the person driving the taxi is the person who's sport is golf##1
 8. the person who's sport is sailing is on the left of the dutch##1
 9. the argentine is on the far right##1
10. the person who's sport is parkour is the person driving the quad-bike##1
11. the person who's hobby is reading is the person watching crime movies##1
12. the mexican is the person driving the helicopter##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |     2     |      3       |      4      |
| Hobby         | camping   | reading | hiking    | rock-climbing  |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel    | crime | horror      | adventure |
| Nationality   | mexican | dutch | malaysian         | argentine  |
| Sport         | sailing  | parkour     | golf | skateboarding     |
| Transport     | helicopter      | quad-bike       | taxi         | train         |

