 3. the person driving the bus is the person who's sport is swimming##1
 4. the person drinking sprite is on the far left##1
 5. the designer is the person who's sport is parkour##1
 6. the person drinking mirinda is the person driving the subway##1
 7. the person who's hobby is photography is the person driving the motorbike##1
 8. the person drinking soy-milk is the teacher##1
 9. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
10. the person who's sport is surfing is the person drinking sprite##1
11. the entrepreneur is on the left of the teacher##1
12. the person driving the motorbike is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
13. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person driving the car##1

.:: Answer ::.
