.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-18::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: hot-chocolate, fanta, almond-milk, lemonade
The people have 4 different hobbies: skydiving, singing, baking, camping
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: family, martial-arts, time-travel, epic
There are 4 different nationalities: argentine, turkish, american, thai
4 different pets are kept: goldfish, bird, pony, dog
 1. the american is on the far left##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is the person watching epic movies##1
 3. the person drinking almond-milk is on the left of the owner of the goldfish##1
 4. the thai is on the left of the argentine##1
 5. the person who's hobby is baking is the person drinking almond-milk##1
 6. the person who's hobby is camping is the person drinking lemonade##1
 7. the person who's hobby is singing is on the right of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
 8. the argentine is on the right of the owner of the dog##1
 9. the owner of the bird is the person watching time-travel movies##1
10. the person watching time-travel movies is on the far left##1
11. the person drinking hot-chocolate is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
12. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |      3       |    4     |
| Beverage      | lemonade       | almond-milk      | fanta      | hot-chocolate    |
| Hobby         | camping | baking | singing | skydiving  |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel    | martial-arts     | epic      | family |
| Nationality   | american  | thai     | argentine    | turkish  |
| Pet           | bird  | dog       | goldfish          | pony      |

