.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-19::.
There 4 different types of food: spinach, pear, peach, avocado
The people have 4 different hobbies: fishing, baking, hiking, woodworking
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: fantasy, disaster, martial-arts, sports
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: soccer, climbing, golf, baseball
The people use 4 different means of transport: snowmobile, train, trike, bike
 1. the person who's sport is golf is on the far left##1
 2. the person eating avocado is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 3. the person driving the trike is the person who's hobby is hiking##1
 4. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the right of the person watching fantasy movies##1
 5. the person watching fantasy movies is on the left of the person driving the bike##1
 6. the person watching sports movies is on the right of the person driving the snowmobile##1
 7. the person driving the bike is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 8. the person who's sport is baseball is on the right of the person eating spinach##1
 9. the person watching disaster movies is on the right of the person eating pear##1
10. the person who's sport is baseball is the person eating peach##1
11. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person eating avocado##1
12. the person who's hobby is baking is on the far right##1
13. the person who's hobby is woodworking is on the right of the person driving the bike##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2     |      3      |       4       |
| Food          | avocado      | pear     | spinach        | peach     |
| Hobby         | hiking     | fishing    | woodworking | baking |
| Movie-Genre   | fantasy | martial-arts  | disaster      | sports       |
| Sport         | golf      | soccer | climbing     | baseball        |
| Transport     | trike   | bike     | snowmobile  | train       |

