.:: Puzzle 5x4-Level-1-20::.
There 4 different types of food: peas, zucchini, pepper, tomato
The people have 4 different hobbies: board-games, camping, reading, singing
The people have 4 different jobs:  electrician, manager, police-officer, fisherman
4 different pets are kept: chinchilla, turtle, rat, bird
The people use 4 different means of transport: tram, skateboard, helicopter, trike
 1. the fisherman is the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 2. the owner of the rat is on the right of the person eating peas##1
 3. the fisherman is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1
 4. the person who's hobby is camping is on the left of the electrician##1
 5. the owner of the rat is the person who's hobby is singing##1
 6. the person eating pepper is on the right of the person who's hobby is camping##1
 7. the person driving the skateboard is on the right of the manager##1
 8. the electrician is the person driving the tram##1
 9. the person eating pepper is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
10. the person eating tomato is the owner of the bird##1
11. the owner of the bird is on the right of the person driving the helicopter##1
12. the owner of the bird is on the left of the police-officer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |       2       |       3        |      4      |
| Food        | zucchini    | tomato        | peas        | pepper      |
| Hobby       | reading       | board-games       | camping      | singing |
| Job         | manager | fisherman | police-officer | electrician      |
| Pet         | chinchilla          | bird         | turtle           | rat    |
| Transport   | helicopter         | skateboard       | trike     | tram   |

 